main event: A UFO report was documented in the Project Blue Book record card, detailing an unidentified aerial phenomenon observed by the witness.
interesting points: The witness described the object as being bright white in color and elongated in shape., The object made no sound during the observation., The witness was sitting in a station wagon on their family farm at the time., The object was first seen at an elevation of 35 degrees and disappeared at an elevation of 18 degrees., The sighting included various forms for collecting detailed information about the observation.
witness description: The witness was 32 years old and was sitting with a friend.
